sequenceDiagram
  participant R as Resource
  participant B as Binding
  participant M as Merger
  participant A as Artifact File

  R->>B: produce fragment (fragmentKey, contentSha256)
  B->>M: emit fragment with resourceId + bindingId
  M->>M: ownerKey = resourceId::fragmentKey
  M->>M: sectionKey = sha256(artifactId + "\0" + ownerKey).slice(0,16)
  M->>A: insert start marker
  M->>A: insert section content
  M->>A: insert end marker

  Note over A: <!-- agent-harness:start section=<sectionKey> owner=<ownerKey> --> ... <!-- agent-harness:end section=<sectionKey> -->
